{"type":"message","id":"8de4be49","parentId":"e8eab783","timestamp":"2026-05-20T19:09:17.822Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[Thu 2026-05-21 03:09 GMT+8] [Subagent Context] You are running as a subagent (depth 1/1). Results auto-announce to your requester; do not busy-poll for status.\n\n[Subagent Task]: 修改 ISAPI 代理，从 header 读取设备 IP：\n\n文件：D:\\astro_py\\astro_hub\\src\\main\\main.py\n\n找到 `_handle_isapi_request` 函数，修改：\n\n当前：\n```python\nasync def _handle_isapi_request(request, path):\n    method = request.method\n    device_ip = request.query_params.get('ip', '192.168.5.72')\n    device = _isapi_devices.get(device_ip, {'username': 'admin', 'password': 'Nftw1357', 'port': 80})\n```\n\n修改为：\n```python\nasync def _handle_isapi_request(request, path):\n    method = request.method\n    # WASM SDK sends deviceIdentify header (format: \"192.168.5.72:80\")\n    device_identify = request.headers.get('deviceIdentify', '')\n    if device_identify and ':' in device_identify:\n        device_ip = device_identify.split(':')[0]\n        device_port = int(device_identify.split(':')[1])\n    else:\n        device_ip = request.query_params.get('ip', '192.168.5.72')\n        device_port = 80\n    \n    device = _isapi_devices.get(device_ip, {'username': 'admin', 'password': 'Nftw1357', 'port': device_port})\n    isapi_url = 'http://{}:{}/ISAPI/{}'.format(device_ip, device['port'], path)\n```\n\n修复后不要过度开发。"}],"timestamp":1779304157813}}
